name: 13 Memory Card - Franz Kohler
description: An Ovcharka Dog who works as an archaeologist is part of an "Ancient Relic" observation team. The team aims to unravel the mystery of the ruins of the future temple "Aeon" buried at the bottom of the sea. Together with his robot assistant, Crayola, they investigate the ritual of summoning aliens and some objects that are believed to be from extraterrestrial origin.
